body:
@cdce8p good find!

I don't think I want to rely on the compat mode because [they seem to want to remove it](https://github.com/pypa/setuptools/blob/09e501feb13e7dd42cc62c7f02e32c4073d61a22/setuptools/command/editable_wheel.py#L78). So I think this is basically https://github.com/python/mypy/issues/13392.

For now I think we should just disable this test and I'm going to leave a comment in the other issue that we should stop supporting editable installs.
